{"tid":2393305,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(3/2 1900)政府就屯門海珠路7號豐景園第一座作出限制與檢測宣告及強制檢測公告","createTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T11:05:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7a2ea7daa0c6f085359ad91e66618279d07d6c","tid":2393305,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/03/P2021020300739.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F03%2FP2021020300739.htm&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjW1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=a447f902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/03/P2021020300739.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1074c8fb070dc3cec640d3f1b69603ca54837d6c","tid":2393305,"uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"政府今日（二月三日）引用《預防及控制疾病（對若干人士強制檢測）規例》（第599J章），作出限制與檢測宣告（下稱「相關宣告」），自下午七時起限制在屯門指明「受限區域」（即屯門海珠路7號豐景園第一座，見附件）內的人士（下稱受檢人士）須留在其處所並接受強制檢測。受檢人士須在其處所等候，直至區內所有已識別的受檢人士完成檢測，而相關檢測結果亦已獲大致確定，方可離開其處所。"},{"pid":"c1c34e17d4f638351ede3ef0cf95bb4694ee9ba8","tid":2393305,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04a54b22b6168fbaf92dcb2a8f68d3f5bd97735","tid":2393305,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"封3跑地盤"},{"pid":"6ceb359d0e1198945cd1d4c838527ac1ff7b6b80","tid":2393305,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b04a54b22b6168fbaf92dcb2a8f68d3f5bd97735","tid":2393305,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"